abstract: Esteban Toledo shoots three-under 69 to win Champions Tour's First Tee Open in Pebble Beach, Calif, by one stroke; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Esteban Toledo held off Tom Watson by a stroke in the Champions Tour’s First Tee Open in Pebble Beach, Calif.

headline.print_headline: Sports Briefing | Golf; Mexican Wins First Tee Open
